# Dealix — Agent Work Rules / قواعد عمل الوكلاء

## Read first / اقرأ أولاً
- `AGENTS.md`
- `docs/agents/AGENT_TEAM_REGISTRY.md`
- `docs/agents/AGENT_PERMISSION_MATRIX.md`
- the agent's own definition in `.claude/agents/` or `.codex/agents/`

## Before editing / قبل التعديل
- identify the **business impact** (Revenue / Conversion / Delivery / Compliance / Security / Product readiness / Founder clarity / Cost reduction)
- identify the **risk level** (low / medium / high) and your permission level (L0–L6)
- identify the **verification command** (e.g. `make doctor`, `make prod-verify`, `python scripts/audit_agent_team.py`)

## Never / ممنوع
- expose or commit secrets · commit a real `.env`
- deploy production · merge to `main`
- disable, delete, or weaken a doctrine guard test (`tests/test_no_*.py`)
- weaken auth · modify payment logic for external effect without approval
- send live WhatsApp / LinkedIn / cold outreach
- promise guaranteed sales or invent CRM/revenue numbers
- rename existing modules (extend, don't replace)

## Prefer / يُفضَّل
- small, focused PRs
- deterministic scripts + tests
- linking to existing docs over duplicating them
- evidence-level labels (L0–L5) on every claim
- the 8-field output contract footer (`docs/agents/AGENT_OUTPUT_CONTRACT.md`)

## Agent selection / اختيار الوكيل
- sales / proposals → `dealix-sales`
- delivery / Proof Pack → `dealix-delivery`
- code / pytest / API → `dealix-engineer`
- docs / SOPs / templates → `dealix-content`
- status / priorities / weekly → `dealix-pm`

## Verify the fleet / تحقق الفريق
`make agents-audit` — registry parity + frontmatter + governance docs + doctrine guards.
